For this episode, I sit down with Matt Farah of @thesmokingtire . Aside from his love for cards, Matt is also huge watch enthusiast with a diverse and gorgeous collection. We dive into where his passion for watches started and to where it has led him with his collection so far! You wont want to miss this episode! Check out the link in my bio to listen to the show on various podcast streaming platforms as well as to watch it on YouTube! Cheers - Eric

node.text:
Excited to finally publish our chat with @thesmokingtire over at @ot.podcast - especially as I’m a long time fan.

We chat about all things car storage, podcasting and YouTubing, and of course - our shared passion for watches. 

What’s this you ask? Well that’s the caseback of Matt’s Rolex Sea-Dweller Deepsea - an ‘issued’ watch, and one of just 50 provided to the ROYAL NAVY CLEARANCE DIVERS. As you can see, it’s #21 - and he’s also got #22 - which is pretty freaking cool.

Go check it out, let me know what you think. 🙏 ✅
